        <p>
            Connecting teachers, students, and parents through a modern
            education management platform.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <section class="about-content">

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>🎯 Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                Our mission is to simplify education management by providing
                a centralized system that improves communication, transparency,
                and efficiency between schools, teachers, students, and parents.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>🚀 Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                To become a trusted digital education platform that empowers
                institutions with smart tools for managing classes, attendance,
                and academic performance in real-time.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>💡 Why EduConnect?</h2>
            <p>
                EduConnect reduces paperwork, saves time, and ensures accurate
                data sharing. Our platform supports better decision-making and
